></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/6372412/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;publication_year=1984&amp;pages=941&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.142.5.941&amp;pmid=6372412">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
        <div class="cover-image flat d-flex justify-content-center flex-column"><div data-is-viewable="" class="cover-image__image"><a href="/toc/radiographics/26/6" title="Go to RadioGraphics " class="d-block"><img src="/cms/10.1148/radiographics.2006.26.issue-6/asset/1463f6a5-6b14-3f6a-56b1-63f6a556b146/cover.jpg" alt="Go to RadioGraphics " loading="lazy"/></a></div></div>
<div class="core-journal-description"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">26</span></span> • <span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">6</span></span> • <span property="datePublished">Nov 1 2006</span></div><div class="core-pagination"><span class="heading">Pages</span>: <span class="content"><span property="pageStart">1637</span> - <span property="pageEnd">1653</span></span></div><div class="core-pmid"><span class="heading">PubMed</span>: <a class="content" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17102041/" property="sameAs" target="_blank" title="Link to PubMed">17102041</a></div></div></div></section><section class="core-copyright"><h4>Copyright</h4><div role="paragraph">© RSNA, 2006.</div></section><section class="core-history"><h4>History</h4><div><b class="core-label">Published online</b>: Nov 1 2006</div></section><section class="core-permissions"><h4>Permissions</h4><div>Request permissions for this article.</div><div><a class="btn" href="https://marketplace.copyright.com/rs-ui-web/mp/search/all/10.1148%2Frg.266065004">Request Permissions</a></div></section><section property="keywords"><h4>Keyword</h4><ol><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=GRE+%3D+gradient+echo&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">GRE = gradient echo</a></li></ol></section><section class="core-article-notes"><h4>Notes</h4><div role="paragraph">The clinical risk factors for fatty liver are reviewed and the pathophysiologic, histologic, epidemiologic, and imaging characteristics are described to aid in the differentiation of fat accumulation from malignancy and from other benign abnormalities in the liver.</div></section></section><section id="tab-contributors" role="tabpanel"><h3>Authors</h3><section class="core-autho