 bilirubin and type 2 diabetes in U.S. South Asian males but not females</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Aayush Visaria</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Alka Kanaya</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Soko Setoguchi</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Meghana Gadgil</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Jaya Satagopan</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Fredirick Lazaro mashili</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">7 February 2024 | PLOS ONE, Vol. 19, No. 2</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0297685">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/B978-0-323-99649-5.00003-0"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/B978-0-323-99649-5.00003-0">Clinical diagnosis and evaluation pathway</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Robert Lam</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Bubu A. Banini</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Albert Do</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Joseph K. Lim</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2024Jan1</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/B978-0-323-99649-5.00003-0">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1590/0100-3984.2024.0009"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1590/0100-3984.2024.0009">Quantificação da gordura hepática: avaliação de diferentes estratégias de medidas pela ressonância magnética nos cas